ISLAMABAD, Apr 24 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Marriyum Aurangzeb on Sunday said the government would strictly enforce law to stop the material that spread chaos in the country.
In a tweet, she said those who spread fascism and disorder during their stay in government and unfurl chaos while atop container were devoid of any positive thinking or public service.
